{"tid":1445072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先喺柏麗嘅人唔該同我入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-11T13:50:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T14:41:32.000Z","uid":219146,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e5ae45481814c0ac5ab1aaec9450ac2ca276b610","tid":1445072,"uid":219146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:50:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">入九公嗰班你地知唔知最後走嗰啲爭啲比你地累死</span></span><br />\n柏麗上九公條路大家都知有樓梯<br />\n入左去前少少就係窄路嚟<br />\n前排入哂去係慢慢行<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">慢慢行呀屌你</span><br />\n知唔知後面仲有好多手足衝緊上去<br />\n我上樓梯嗰陣已經係最後排<br />\n後面一個人都冇<br />\n逼到入閘口之前啲人仲散步<br />\n我地唔係行公園呀<br />\n後面係咁叫行快啲佢地都仲係遊花園咁<br />\n可唔可以唔好再累手足比人拉"},{"pid":"0f97903e80be74c449fb1e3200799d371af86fdb","tid":1445072,"uid":219146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:53:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"006d072eea9ef43f28eb87425abee813dc15c27b","tid":1445072,"uid":219146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:54:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f8d4f96f243776e3d6130789a8e227abe39640c2","tid":1445072,"uid":219146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:58:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16dede4649a9f164f3d93b89e3dc2ef39c82e0b1","tid":1445072,"uid":219146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:59:53.000Z","msg":"sorry 語氣重左<br />\n不過唔該以後要撤退嗰陣真係行快少少<br />\n如果唔係走最後嗰啲真係好危險<br />\n我地唔可以再失去任何一個手足"},{"pid":"ebf31eabcda4103abe7f205626f60000f58563be","tid":1445072,"uid":219146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:00:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53aed2c29aa2251b293951ceadc8854c0a6a4875","tid":1445072,"uid":202937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:01:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8740f13c8e48abc2743a49769f534c253b161a06","tid":1445072,"uid":219146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:08:47.000Z","msg":"仲有中間勁多人拎住支水